short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Grilime tab pro is a Chrome extension that transforms your new browser tab into a personalized dashboard.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Grilime Tab Pro Search enhances your browser by implementing its advanced search engine as the default. Search results and advertisements are provided by trusted partners, ensuring a secure and efficient browsing experience through HTTP redirects.

By selecting "Add to Chrome," you agree to install the "Grilime Tab Pro Search" extension, set it as your default search engine in Chrome, and accept the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

For more information, please visit:
- Privacy Policy: https://grilimetabproapp.com/home/p.html
- Terms of Use: https://grilimetabproapp.com/home/tu.html
- About: https://grilimetabproapp.com/home/au.html
- Contact: https://grilimetabproapp.com/home/cu.html
